  "short_description": "2 Late 2 Evade is a driving game inspired by different road movies. Cover the maximum distance in heavy traffic at the highest possible speed. Use the temporary state of slow motion to avoid crashing. Compete a tour across iconic and treacherous roads. Pick a car, customize it and just hit the road.",
