  "detailed_description": "In 2 Late 2 Evade, all you have are your driving skills to ride at high speed between other cars on the most dangerous roads. There are no rules and no allies in the deserts, canyons and forests.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068320/extras/dd747ac2964e156c8fbb18d0c95ba847.poster.avif?t=1723464354\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068320/extras/dd747ac2964e156c8fbb18d0c95ba847.webm?t=1723464354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068320/extras/dd747ac2964e156c8fbb18d0c95ba847.mp4?t=1723464354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Experience nonstop action</strong> - Pick a car & jump into an action-packed journey. Face extreme environments in a richly created world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068320/extras/887fe169ed33f89fbd3a2aa70d4152d5.poster.avif?t=1723464354\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068320/extras/887fe169ed33f89fbd3a2aa70d4152d5.webm?t=1723464354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068320/extras/887fe169ed33f89fbd3a2aa70d4152d5.mp4?t=1723464354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Your car, your identity</strong> - 15 unique vehicles to unlock and customize. Personalize your bodywork with fresh paint jobs to show off your car to the world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068320/extras/8e768e7c0784232b4715713b7356bac2.poster.avif?t=1723464354\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068320/extras/8e768e7c0784232b4715713b7356bac2.webm?t=1723464354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068320/extras/8e768e7c0784232b4715713b7356bac2.mp4?t=1723464354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Capture the heart-pounding moments</strong> - Unleash your creativity and share your epic in-game snapshots with the world. Get ready to capture the speed, style, and spectacle in every frame!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068320/extras/07d59c8c33f54bd4dc4d7d6d5aa87d1c.poster.avif?t=1723464354\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068320/extras/07d59c8c33f54bd4dc4d7d6d5aa87d1c.webm?t=1723464354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068320/extras/07d59c8c33f54bd4dc4d7d6d5aa87d1c.mp4?t=1723464354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Test your handling skills</strong> - Enter the temporary state of slow motion and turn your vehicle at excessive angles. Fight your way using skill and tons of nitrous.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068320/extras/413667d937bdb78d00a0d1dc5f21ae95.poster.avif?t=1723464354\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068320/extras/413667d937bdb78d00a0d1dc5f21ae95.webm?t=1723464354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068320/extras/413667d937bdb78d00a0d1dc5f21ae95.mp4?t=1723464354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
